3: Enter "SFO" in the search box and select "San Francisco, CA - Airport (SFO)".
4: Click on the "Pickup" filter and select "April 2023".
5: Click on the "Return" filter and select "April 24, 2023".
6: Select the SUVs and Wagons option.
7: Click on the search button to find available vehicles.
8: Click on the "Make" filter and select "SUV".
9: Click on the "Model" filter and select "Wagon".
10: Click on "Next day & Next-day rentals" to filter results for vehicles available for pick-up on the next day.
